Musictrade music video

This is a music video on Doc's fresh Pirate Bay track. The song and the video are dedicated to The Pirate Bay and to the cool people behind it. The video utilizes sounds and images from the recent trial against The Pirate Bay activists and from the events surrounding the trial. The trial was coined Spectrial by the Swedish pirates.
